<i>I'll even eat a bean pie
I don't mind</i>

189
00:06:43,738 --> 00:06:45,031
<i>Me and missy is so early</i>

190
00:06:45,114 --> 00:06:46,783
<i>Busy, busy making money</i>

191
00:06:47,450 --> 00:06:48,910
<i>All right!</i>

