00:10:41,058 --> 00:10:42,184
and it's not important?

295
00:10:42,268 --> 00:10:43,561
Come on, do I look like
I was born yesterday?

296
00:10:43,644 --> 00:10:44,854
I just said
it's not important.

297
00:10:44,937 --> 00:10:46,314
And I'm sorry
I left you hanging,

298
00:10:46,397 --> 00:10:47,648
but you wouldn't even have
this job without me.

299
00:10:47,732 --> 00:10:49,900
And I wouldn't even need this
job if it weren't for you.

300
00:10:49,984 --> 00:10:51,402
So, what's your problem?

301
00:10:52,111 --> 00:10:53,404
I'm sorry, Kevin.
I'm...

